{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Apocalypse Island</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Survive. Explore. Fight.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the shoes of an ex-scientist thrust into a harrowing mission on a desolate land overrun by the undead. This First-Person Survival Open World adventure challenges you to fight for your life against relentless zombies while uncovering the island's dark secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274800/extras/Video_12-02-25__14_59_35.gif?t=1739385555\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf3f <strong>Open World Exploration:</strong> Traverse lush forests, abandoned cities, and mysterious locations filled with hidden dangers and valuable resources.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf7d\ufe0f <strong>Survival Mechanics:</strong> Manage your hunger, thirst, fatigue, and health. Scavenge for food, drinks, and supplies to stay alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274800/extras/Video_12-02-25__14_56_52_1_.gif?t=1739385555\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf32 <strong>Resource Gathering &amp; Crafting:</strong> Loot the environment to find materials, craft essential items, and build shelters to protect yourself from both the undead and the harsh elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274800/extras/Video_12-02-25__14_58_06.gif?t=1739385555\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f <strong>Diverse Arsenal:</strong> Start with your trusty Hunting Hatchet and discover powerful weapons like axes, swords, and firearms as you explore deeper into the island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274800/extras/Video_12-02-25__14_58_49.gif?t=1739385555\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf3f <strong>Realistic Needs System:</strong> Experience the struggle of true survival\u2014hunt wildlife, cook raw meat, gather vegetables, and secure fresh water to sustain yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you ready to face the horrors lurking on <i>Apocalypse Island</i>? Your survival depends on it.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3274800?t=1739385555","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3274800?t=1739385555","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274800/83fad6e189dfd6dd20785ce2c2c6db283de1e5f0/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739385555","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274800/83fad6e189dfd6dd20785ce2c2c6db283de1e5f0/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739385555","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Apocalypse Island</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Survive. Explore. Fight.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the shoes of an ex-scientist thrust into a harrowing mission on a desolate land overrun by the undead. This First-Person Survival Open World adventure challenges you to fight for your life against relentless zombies while uncovering the island's dark secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274800/extras/Video_12-02-25__14_59_35.gif?t=1739385555\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf3f <strong>Open World Exploration:</strong> Traverse lush forests, abandoned cities, and mysterious locations filled with hidden dangers and valuable resources.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf7d\ufe0f <strong>Survival Mechanics:</strong> Manage your hunger, thirst, fatigue, and health. Scavenge for food, drinks, and supplies to stay alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274800/extras/Video_12-02-25__14_56_52_1_.gif?t=1739385555\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf32 <strong>Resource Gathering &amp; Crafting:</strong> Loot the environment to find materials, craft essential items, and build shelters to protect yourself from both the undead and the harsh elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274800/extras/Video_12-02-25__14_58_06.gif?t=1739385555\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f <strong>Diverse Arsenal:</strong> Start with your trusty Hunting Hatchet and discover powerful weapons like axes, swords, and firearms as you explore deeper into the island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274800/extras/Video_12-02-25__14_58_49.gif?t=1739385555\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf3f <strong>Realistic Needs System:</strong> Experience the struggle of true survival\u2014hunt wildlife, cook raw meat, gather vegetables, and secure fresh water to sustain yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you ready to face the horrors lurking on <i>Apocalypse Island</i>? Your survival depends on it.</p>","developers":["Bettini Games"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Free To Play","id":"37"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274800/header.jpg?t=1739385555","is_free":true,"legal_notice":"Tutti i diritti del gioco riservati ad Alessandro Bettini.","linux_requireme